{"tid":1989233,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"日本人收入統計分享（日本官方資料），節錄左d常用數據比大家睇下","createTime":"2020-04-25T19:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T07:56:35.000Z","uid":244066,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fbee3990f3d29c6c963e50370b28d4fee7867592","tid":1989233,"uid":244066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T19:08:24.000Z","msg":"日本每年都會出一份好詳細既收入報告，所以可以大概知道日本普遍人到底搵幾多錢<br />\n如果只係想知東京，將個表所有數x1.23就得<br />\n因為東京都平均收入係全國收入1.23倍，方便d當標準差一樣就將所有數x1.23（大都市都會好似香港咁有極高收入既人存在，所以可能實際普通人收入同其他地區唔係有太大分別，但冇數據所以冇得估）<br />\n另外日本人大約只有唔夠8成收入係實際收入（香港係超過9成）<br />\n<br />\n1. 日本人平均收入<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mhlw.go.jp/toukei/itiran/roudou/chingin/kouzou/z2019/dl/01.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mhlw.go.jp%2Ftoukei%2Fitiran%2Froudou%2Fchingin%2Fkouzou%2Fz2019%2Fdl%2F01.pdf&d=lW7zubw4D25L16l94wxnCtmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=3afcd570\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mhlw.go.jp/toukei/itiran/roudou/chingin/kouzou/z2019/dl/01.pdf</a><br />\n．2019年日本人平均收入係$22,180（東京係$27,280）<br />\n．作為比較，香港人平均收入約$26,125（根據2016年人口統計報告將收入按十等分計算推斷，再加入2019年到2016年薪金升幅得出）<br />\n．利用第5點既文件可以推斷出日本人收入中位數約$19,670（香港為$19,000）<br />\n<br />\n2. 年齡與收入關係<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mhlw.go.jp/toukei/itiran/roudou/chingin/kouzou/z2019/dl/02.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mhlw.go.jp%2Ftoukei%2Fitiran%2Froudou%2Fchingin%2Fkouzou%2Fz2019%2Fdl%2F02.pdf&d=lW7zubw4D25L16l94wxnCtmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=b99505b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mhlw.go.jp/toukei/itiran/roudou/chingin/kouzou/z2019/dl/02.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 學歷、年齡與收入關係<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mhlw.go.jp/toukei/itiran/roudou/chingin/kouzou/z2019/dl/03.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mhlw.go.jp%2Ftoukei%2Fitiran%2Froudou%2Fchingin%2Fkouzou%2Fz2019%2Fdl%2F03.pdf&d=lW7zubw4D25L16l94wxnCtmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=c74db5f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mhlw.go.jp/toukei/itiran/roudou/chingin/kouzou/z2019/dl/03.pdf</a><br />\n．大學畢業生不論男女平均薪金$16,300（香港八大約$20,000，所有大學畢業生約$16,000）<br />\n．大學畢業男人30-34歲平均搵$23,200、女人30-34歲平均搵$20,200<br />\n．大學畢業男人係50-54歲搵最多錢，平均搵$38,580<br />\n<br />\n4. 職業、年齡與收入關係<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mhlw.go.jp/toukei/itiran/roudou/chingin/kouzou/z2019/dl/05.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mhlw.go.jp%2Ftoukei%2Fitiran%2Froudou%2Fchingin%2Fkouzou%2Fz2019%2Fdl%2F05.pdf&d=lW7zubw4D25L16l94wxnCtmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=1aef1235\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mhlw.go.jp/toukei/itiran/roudou/chingin/kouzou/z2019/dl/05.pdf</a><br />\n．男人做金融保險搵最多，平均搵$33,280<br />\n．女人做教育搵最多，平均搵$22,860<br />\n<br />\n5. 所有年齡層不同月入的百分比<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mhlw.go.jp/toukei/itiran/roudou/chingin/kouzou/z2019/dl/07.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mhlw.go.jp%2Ftoukei%2Fitiran%2Froudou%2Fchingin%2Fkouzou%2Fz2019%2Fdl%2F07.pdf&d=lW7zubw4D25L16l94wxnCtmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=e75e72b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mhlw.go.jp/toukei/itiran/roudou/chingin/kouzou/z2019/dl/07.pdf</a><br />\n．月入$38,270就可以成為日本最高收入10%既男人（女人為$26,280）<br />\n．20-24歲最高收入既10%男性搵$18,820（女性為$18,600）<br />\n．25-29歲最高收入既10%男性搵$23,110（女性為$21,700）<br />\n．FG(20-24歲)搵$30,000或以上只佔0.3%男性（女性為0.1%）<br />\n<br />\n6. 日本各地區平均收入<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mhlw.go.jp/toukei/itiran/roudou/chingin/kouzou/z2019/dl/08.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mhlw.go.jp%2Ftoukei%2Fitiran%2Froudou%2Fchingin%2Fkouzou%2Fz2019%2Fdl%2F08.pdf&d=lW7zubw4D25L16l94wxnCtmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=0403ebbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mhlw.go.jp/toukei/itiran/roudou/chingin/kouzou/z2019/dl/08.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇返統計，日本人係2001年既時候收入係最高，之後不升反跌<br />\n去到上年2019年，18年黎平均薪金係冇高過<br />\n香港人工近幾年都已經超越左日本甚至接近東京...成件事都真係幾sad"},{"pid":"6d2e8fe943ce75545ab99a60c44998e209f11801","tid":1989233,"uid":7206,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T19:16:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">．女人做教育搵最多，平均搵$22,860<br />\n</span><br />\n課外授業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ca3494a30c6753261811ab617aac9f0ebf22f4","tid":1989233,"uid":185606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T19:28:48.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"711edfdbe3f4d18397cb95db80168f244c71bc17","tid":1989233,"uid":60344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T19:49:34.000Z","msg":"strong post"},{"pid":"98f6d21062955c00510be3ed7033671dd0538bc4","tid":1989233,"uid":114159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T20:28:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">FG(20-24歲)搵$30,000或以上只佔0.3%男性（女性為0.1%）</span><br />\n連登FG: 渣ga"},{"pid":"3952ed634aa317b98808ea0fda178050c2dc304a","tid":1989233,"uid":70183,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T20:31:54.000Z","msg":"你講人地收入呢十幾年無點變<br />\n<br />\n但係人地國內物價都同樣冇點變喎"},{"pid":"8cf7bdb4ac268ea4fe1a8346b65029c49f7330af","tid":1989233,"uid":64073,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T00:26:09.000Z","msg":"計實收定係名義上人工？<br />\n<br />\n日本出糧好似係預先扣晒退休金保險稅<br />\n而且車費多數公司出埋<br />\n出幾多可以用幾多<br />\n<br />\n日本FG一般可以喺搬出嚟住/儲錢二揀一<br />\n香港FG唔月光已經好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d8f03bc28ab9ff5315b5d42989adf7c2a01a12","tid":1989233,"uid":244066,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"3952ed634aa317b98808ea0fda178050c2dc304a","tid":1989233,"uid":70183,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T20:31:54.000Z","msg":"你講人地收入呢十幾年無點變<br />\n<br />\n但係人地國內物價都同樣冇點變喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T04:37:36.000Z","msg":"香港物價真心唔算高<br />\n當然樓價已經跑贏所有城市<br />\n以已發展地區黎計，香港人人工升幅應係前列"},{"pid":"165e961e6b597a5d64a512658450aeb043581985","tid":1989233,"uid":244066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cf7bdb4ac268ea4fe1a8346b65029c49f7330af","tid":1989233,"uid":64073,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T00:26:09.000Z","msg":"計實收定係名義上人工？<br />\n<br />\n日本出糧好似係預先扣晒退休金保險稅<br />\n而且車費多數公司出埋<br />\n出幾多可以用幾多<br />\n<br />\n日本FG一般可以喺搬出嚟住/儲錢二揀一<br />\n香港FG唔月光已經好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T04:38:17.000Z","msg":"依個係名義上人工<br />\n所以實收大約打8折"},{"pid":"7f04da2709e277eb184a9b9897c72f7bfbe862ad","tid":1989233,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T04:45:16.000Z","msg":"屌，好撚窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不要再說了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9020e956896704d3151e947250f2583cb6a269c","tid":1989233,"uid":153811,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T07:56:35.000Z","msg":"其實d 人話香港人工麻麻根本係缺乏國際視野，<br />\n而又班連登仔因為現實倒霉，網上扮到一個月6,7月以上收入，亦都係吹到上天花板。<br />\n<br />\n基本上連登仔收入已經去到瑞士既中位數以上。"}]}